    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this vehicle from day one, keeping it garage-parked and meticulously detailed. You won't find a single blemish on it. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale to a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate such a well-kept ride. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
