    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition is a testament to fastidious ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further enhanced by a multi-layer ceramic coating. The alloy wheels are flawless, with no curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under original floor mats, and it has never been smoked in. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is detailed to a show-standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is an investment-quality example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
